  <td><span class="arc-tag tag-sam">SAM</span><span class="arc-tag tag-madoria">MADORIA</span>
  Sam's second encounter with May at a Death Jazz event — this time with military colleagues. He spots the Lurker beside May in the crowd, watching her. The Lurker says to Sam: <em>"Oh, you're looking for the girl, right? Sidney? She's right there."</em> Sam throws a reality battery at the Lurker, sucking him into a portal. May spots Sam and runs to him: <em>"It's you again — I searched everywhere for you. Who even are you? Do I know you?"</em> Sam warns her of a coming threat. He is pulled back through a portal by an unknown force — leaving behind a drawing that looks like Sidney. May stares at it: <em>"I know now,"</em> with wet eyes. She straightens up. Moves forward. Furious.
  <div class="lore-note">📌 The Lurker knows about Sidney and Sam's connection. He taunts Sam with it — not out of cruelty, but because the Lurker enjoys chaos and is always collecting information. He is obsessed with the Madness inside May. Sidney is connected to that Madness. He is 5 steps ahead on this too.</div></td></tr>

