  <div class="lore-note">📌 THE REVEAL: The Lurker has been the front. The Tenebris has been the war. The Sentry has delivered its master's declaration. Death now knows the full shape of what he is fighting. It is larger than the Lurker. It is older than the Lurker. It has been planning since before either of them existed. This is Arc 2's enemy — and it has just been named.</div></td></tr>

