  <div class="lore-note green">📌 IZA: This is his most important moment. He doesn't understand Elystria's note. He keeps it anyway. This is Theme 4 — cherish the things close to us, even when we don't understand them. The Gardener of Creation secret lives in his pocket.</div></td></tr>

