  <div class="lore-note green">📌 CRYIOUS: He knows Vivian's father's legacy is still alive in the garden. He will never tell him. He believes some things must be found by the person they belong to. He files it beside the names he recites and keeps going. This is Cryious — duty and tenderness folded into the same absolute loyalty.</div></td></tr>

